text: Sajjad Zareeian Jahromi (; born 22 September 1997, in Tehran) is an Iranian professional squash player. As of February 2018, he was ranked number 143 in the world. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male squash players Category:Squash players at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Iran
